    "## 🧪 Troubleshooting MCP\n",
    "\n",
    "### ❌ Erreur: `Server not found` ou `Connection refused`\n",
    "**Cause**: Le serveur MCP n'est pas accessible\n",
    "**Solution**:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "# Pour un serveur local: vérifier que le script existe\n",
    "ls resources/mcp_local_server.py\n",
    "\n",
    "# Pour un serveur distant: vérifier l'URL\n",
    "curl -I https://mcp.kiwi.com\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### ❌ Erreur: `Tool execution failed`\n",
    "**Cause**: Un tool a échoué lors de l'exécution\n",
    "**Solution**:\n",
    "```python\n",
    "# Ajouter du logging pour voir l'erreur exacte\n",
    "import logging\n",
    "logging.basicConfig(level=logging.DEBUG)\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### ❌ Erreur: `asyncio.TimeoutError`\n",
    "**Cause**: Le serveur met trop de temps à répondre\n",
    "**Solution**:\n",
    "```python\n",
    "# Augmenter le timeout\n",
    "response = await asyncio.wait_for(\n",
    "    agent.ainvoke(...),\n",
    "    timeout=60  # Augmenter de 30 à 60 secondes\n",
    ")\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "### ❌ Erreur: `uvx command not found`\n",
    "**Cause**: Astral package manager n'est pas installé\n",
    "**Solution**:\n",
    "```bash\n",
    "# Installer uvx\n",
    "curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh\n",
    "```"
   ]
